org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.tools.offlineImageViewer

Class FSImageLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hdfs.tools.offlineImageViewer.FSImageLoader

  •  class FSImageLoader
extends Object
    FSImageLoader loads fsimage and provide methods to return JSON formatted file status of the namespace of the fsimage.
